config BR2_PACKAGE_PARTED
	bool "parted"
        select BR2_PACKAGE_UTIL_LINUX
	help
          GNU Parted is a program for creating, destroying, resizing, checking and copying partitions,
          and the file systems on them. This is useful for creating space for new operating systems,
          reorganising disk usage, copying data between hard disks and disk imaging.

          http://www.gnu.org/software/parted/
